criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients undergoing cardiac surgery were prospectively enrolled.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  History of End Stage Renal Disease or on Dialysis;

          -  prior kidney transplantation;

          -  patients with a DNR order;

          -  pregnancy;

          -  moribund patients with expected death within 24 h or whose survival to 28 days was
             unlikely due to an uncontrollable comorbidity (i.e., end-stage liver or heart disease,
             untreatable malignancy)
